snippet.title: True Crime And Chill - About Alex and Amber
snippet.description:
Meet your hostesses!

Each week, Alex and Amber will present true crime cases for information and speculation. Who were the victims? What really happened?

Here is our introduction to learn a little bit about us before we take you on journeys through the rabbit hole!

🔎For case notes, credits, links to videos, and more visit our website:
https://truecrimeandchill.com/

----------------------------------
